      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i dont really want to deal with the whole doctor thing right now, it takes forever to get an appointment. how bad is the interaction really? like if i just finish my current bottle of sertraline and then start the st johns wort right after, is that okay? i just wanna get off the meds and get back to feeling normal.",
